<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='561000' id='t-561000'>But -- and it's a big but --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='564000' id='t-564000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='566000' id='t-566000'>it turns out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568000' id='t-568000'>when you look at the methods used by industry-funded trials,</span>
