<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='607000' id='t-607000'>This is something called funnel plot.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609000' id='t-609000'>And a funnel plot is a very clever way of spotting</span>
