<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:10
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='659000' id='t-659000'>That's how you can prove it statistically,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='661000' id='t-661000'>but what about stories?</span>
